<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَقَال إِنْ شِئْتَ حَبَسْتَ أَصْلَهَا وَتَصَدَّقْتَ بِهَا <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَقَال جَابِرٌ: لَمْ يَكُنْ أَحَدٌ مِنْ أَصْحَابِ النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ ذُو مَقْدِرَةٍ إِلاَّ وَقَفَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَتَفْصِيلُهُ فِي مُصْطَلَحِ <span class="c2">(صَدَقَةٌ - وَقْفٌ)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>تَسْجِيلٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> تَوْثِيقٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
